title: NFL Week 13 recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 13 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- recap every Sunday game on the Week 13 NFL schedule. Highlights include Brady vs. Rodgers, Johnny Football's first TD and the Chargers' comeback.
